  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个静态网站托管的架构图，从用户浏览器到S3的完整链路。核心是用CloudFront做CDN加速，Route53做DNS解析。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "CDN",
        "DNS",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这是一个典型的无服务器静态托管方案。我先把四个主要子系统框出来：用户浏览器、Route53、CloudFront和S3存储桶。每个用不同颜色区分可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，蓝色给浏览器，黄色给DNS，粉色给CDN，绿色给存储。另外注意浏览器节点要标注成\"Browser\"，别写\"User\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，USER节点已设为Browser，四个子图颜色也配好了。现在我在Route53里面放一个A记录别名节点，CloudFront那边需要展开哪些组件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "DNS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CloudFront里面要有四层：Edge Locations做边缘节点入口，Lambda@Edge处理基础认证，ACM证书管TLS，最后还有Cache层。认证逻辑要标注清楚是Basic Auth。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "CDN子图已展开，四层结构都加上了。S3那边我放了Origin Access Identity和Static Files，OAI用来限制直接访问。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OAI",
        "FILES",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "链路连接这样走：浏览器HTTPS到Route53的A记录，然后跳到Edge Locations，依次经过Lambda@Edge、证书验证、缓存层，最后通过OAI身份访问S3文件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "连接都画好了。我在浏览器到R53的线上标注了HTTPS，CACHE到OAI的线标注了\"OAI Only\"强调安全策略。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，R53到EDGE那条线我没让你标文字，保持无标签就行。还有证书节点要注明TLS 1.2+的版本要求。",
